>
> 73 is the 1st year the fuse box moved to the center.  When the turn
signals moved up above the headlights, the
> fuse box had to be moved.  70 thru 72, the fuse box was above the
headlight on the left. Each year, 70-72, has
> a different fuse box and the wiring to them and the relays hanging out the
bottom are different.
> 72 bus = 411 937 505 C
> and if you are wondering about D and E:
> 73 411 = 411 937 505 D
